  "text": "\"All included studies were planned to be assessed independently by two authors for methodological quality using the Cochrane and risk of bias tools; however, this was not achieved as there was only one paper that reported such information [CITATION_1] \". Two independent authors assessed the studies to be included based on the eligibility and relevance criteria only.",
